## тАЬActive flagsтАЭ definition (must confirm)
Backend must define `activeFlags` consistently with frontend expectations:
- Option A (recommended): count of flags that have at least one enabled rule in any environment
- Option B: count of flags enabled in the тАЬProductionтАЭ environment only
- Option C: count of flags with any evaluations in the window

Pick one and implement it in both:
- `summary.activeFlags`
- `summary.activeFlagsDeltaPct`

